data.value: Choose delicate sparkle when you wear the Sparkling Huggie Hoop Earrings. An essential for every collection, these sterling silver hoop earrings are set with a row of clear cubic zirconia. Versatile and classic, these hoops make a winning gift or addition to your own look. Whether you wear them solo for subtle sparkle or stack them up your ear with other styles, these staple hoop earrings will elevate your everyday.
